{
  "stem": "8370.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And eventually, I would say one hour before we landed in Auschwitz, one of the prisoners, who was in Auschwitz who escaped from the camp and was re-arrested, he say, yes, I know.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I recognize.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We are going to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We arrive on a ramp, offloading ramp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they told us to disembark, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we came to the camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was night.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we receive nothing to eat during the day, nothing to eat--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing, nothing.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not even water.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was from about eight o'clock in the morning till about nine, 10 o'clock evenings, so even no water.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we arrived to the concentration camp, we put, they put us in-- we marched about three, three kilometers from the offloading ramp.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This time was not ramp as is today in Birkenau in the middle of the camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was outside.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We saw only the big chimneys, plenty of fire and smoke going out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was-- afterwards, I realized it was a crematorium working at night.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we are, I, I personally accepted this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's, oh, a bakery is working-- for the beginning, you know, my first impression was.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then early morning, arrive people who have taken our particulars, you know, and filled the records for each of us.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then, of course, they put a tattoo on the arm.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there was only one concentration camp who puts tattoo with a number on your arm.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know, it was due to the fact that we had no ID papers on us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And to know, and they-- it was a such a quantity of people dying every day that it was impossible to keep a proper record, who is alive and who is dead.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So the only way to keep a record was to numbered us.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
